    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that, but honestly the clinics are so expensive and the wait times are insane. it's probably just a bad sprain, right? i can barely put any weight on it but if i just wrap it tight and keep it up, shouldn't that be enough to get the swelling down? i'm pretty sure i can just manage it at home for a week or so.",
