    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i just dont have the time or money for a clinic right now. if i take some heavy ibuprofen and just keep it iced and elevated for the next 3-4 days, is there anything stopping that from working? like, is it really that much of a risk if i just wait to see if it gets better on its own?",
